  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5311995/" class="title-link">《画家生涯》：文人画家的“去伪化”</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5311995"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/jeffyanguang/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1085884-29.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jeffyanguang/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">严杰夫</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-02-19"
      class="main-meta">2012-02-19 20:51:37</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5311995_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  文/严杰夫  长久以来，自董其昌在山水画上提出“南北宗论”后，文人画画家总是以一副“悦诗书以求道，洒翰墨以怡情”（王直语）的形象出现。这种“纵情绘事”的居士形象，与“惟涂抹一山一水，一草一木，即悬之市中，以易斗米”（董其昌语）的所谓职业画师，被严格区分开来，最...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5311995/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">8有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5311995_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5311995_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










